# draftbit-maps

react native maps wrapped for draftbit

## Installation

```sh
npm install draftbit-maps
```

## Usage

```js
import DraftbitMaps from "draftbit-maps";

// ...

const result = await DraftbitMaps.multiply(3, 7);
```
